$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_open

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_open -  This function tells you whether an object is open or closed.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_open()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
Return 1 if open, 0 if closed.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/close_lock.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function tells you whether an object is open or closed.
It returns 1 if the object is open and 0 if the object is closed.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_open(), set_closed()

.EP

